	U.S. Generic Pharmaceuticals


	 manufacturing sites are in Chestnut Ridge, New York; Huntsville, Alabama; Irvine, California; Rochester, Michigan; and Chennai, India; which handle the production, assembly, quality assurance testing and packaging of our products.  We estimate that, for the products we manufacture, our U.S. facilities contributed over


	95%


	 of our manufacturing production based on revenue compared to fewer than


	5%


