	 to fully impair a license intangible asset related to OPANA



	®



	 ER as well as charges of


	$4.3 million


	 to completely write off certain miscellaneous property, plant and equipment. These impairment charges were recorded because we determined the carrying amounts of these assets were no longer recoverable.




