	Equal to or above 40



	th



	 percentile but below 50



	th



	 percentile






	0.5








	Below 40



	th



	 percentile






	0










	In the event that Relative TSR over the TSR Performance Period is negative, the multiple applicable to the TSR Target Performance Award shall not exceed 1.






