Delivering quality medicines,
Helping patients in need
 Learn more about Endo International plc










A Highly Focused Generics and Specialty Branded Pharmaceutical Company
At Endo International, our generics and specialty branded products play an important role in helping millions of patients lead healthier lives. Through our operating companies, we are dedicated to delivering quality medicines to patients in need through excellence in development, manufacturing and commercialization.






Learn More About Our Companies






